Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,THE GRAND SORCERER MATORIV
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! You have to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything to do with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Matoriv!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how you've grown!\NYou're ripe for motorboarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.\NI've changed your diaper, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a motorboard greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all, you lech.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you know this guy, Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't just know him. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Matoriv! Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mage who fought the Dark Lord with the\NHero and served the Papnica royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was the Grand Sorcerer Matoriv!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By Hero, you mean Master Avan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Uncle Matoriv was\Nin Master Avan's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your mother, Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's still single, I can marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to visit our home a lot,\Nbut I had no idea he was hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This old lech was in the Hero's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I wouldn't want to\Nsee him, but not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could be more helpful\Nthan the Grand Sorcerer Matoriv!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Sir Matoriv!\NHelp us rescue Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The Princess of Papnica\Nis being held on Valge Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Sir Matoriv can overcome\Nthe enemy's strange spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done helping the stupid royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The royal family? Stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just the royal family.\NIt's people in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Dark Army was attacking, they'd\Nbutter us up so we'd fight for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But once peace came, they all suddenly\Nturned their backs on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I got to be advisor to the king\Nafter the battle was over,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was constantly badgered\Nby the other officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they were all\Njealous of my skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's people for you.\NThey think about nothing but themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew tired of all of them\Nand decided to live in this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved you all out of a whim,\Nbut that's as far as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, even if I help you, once it's\Nover, you'll just forget about me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everybody thinks\Nabout nothing but themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Master Avan's companion,\Nyou should know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Avan?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They have the same eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dai! Master Avan's last student!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,His last?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan gave his life to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Avan is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we want to avenge his death\Nby defeating the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Lend us your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Legendary Forbidden Magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think Flazzard mentioned\Nsomething like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Forbidden Magic is magic so dirty\Nthat its use is banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who uses it\Nbecomes a pariah among Mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we save Princess Leona?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you break\Nthe Blizzblaze Curse Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, you have to approach outside\Nthe field and destroy these two Spires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need bombs that pack a hefty punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You can use\Nwhatever you like for materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget they need\Nto pack a hefty punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need any silly bombs.\NI can blow them away with my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a Student of Avan, too, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He is. This is Popp, the Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Does he show promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the opposite. I've never seen\Na Mage who looked so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do something,\Nhe's going to die out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me. I'll train him with\Na Special Hard Course worse than Avan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say, Lord Hadlar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A full-on assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sure to attempt to destroy\Nthe Dark Flame and Dark Ice Spires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When they do,\Nthey'll split up their forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We will gather all of our armies\Nand wipe out Dai and his companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But Flazzard is sure to complain\Nabout not being able to take credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster that I created\Nusing Legendary Forbidden Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's basically my son.\NHe won't disobey his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. At last,\Nmy Dragon Legion can play a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Baran. I have something else\NI need you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystvearn is fighting Carl Kingdom,\Nbut they're proving quite resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to take down Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said "all of our armies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And defeating the Hero should take\Nprecedence over other invasions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why the Six Legion Commanders\Nwere summoned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is there some other reason\Nyou don't want me to face this boy, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you will, the order still stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll let you give the orders\Nthis time, Dark Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to Carl Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's so special about Baran that Lord\NHadlar gives him preferential treatment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even Baran can\Noverthrow Carl that easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must kill Dai before that happens!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall make Valge Island their grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell?! This is Nayle Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the\NInstant Transmission Spell, Rura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You think of your destination\Nand it takes you there instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Matoriv, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Leira, long time no see.\NI ran into Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotten all curvy,\Njust like you when you were young!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here with Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complicated. I figured\NI'd give his butt a well-deserved kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get over here.\N-I get it, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems like a mean old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he's teaching,\NI know Popp will grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was once called\Nthe greatest of all Mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can be a little quirky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really going to\Nlet me use powerful magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, this is basic stamina building\Nbefore training. It's a warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Better pick up the pace\Nor you'll get trampled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mera doesn't work well under water!\NFind another way out or you'll drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna know how? You don't use a spell!\NYou release your Magic Power itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,From your entire body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. Did I read him wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop.\NYour wounds haven't fully healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pushing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I can't rest\Nwhen Popp is out there training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Matoriv said this training\Nwould help me to fight Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never forgive Flazzard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just when I finally found Leona!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat him!\NAnd I swear I'll rescue Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen Dai so emotional before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Leona must\Nreally be important to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.39,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.40,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}FIVE FINGER FLARES{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole day together and\Nyour Magic Power increased just that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be ashamed a hundred year-old\Nlike me beat a youngster like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading back to Papnica.\NUse your own Rura spell to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy. You flew from the river to\Nthe shore by releasing your Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a clear image of your\Ndestination, Rura's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the river to the shore and\Nfrom here to Papnica is totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Beside, even if I learn Rura,\Nit's useless in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your head out of your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mage's magic is\Nfor protecting his companions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thwarting danger using numerous spells\Nand knowledge is what a Mage does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize,\Nif you could have used Rura,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you could have rescued your companions\Nfrom the burning Balloon Ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like you're anything more\Nthan a novice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't clear a challenge this easy,\Nyou'll just drag everyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you join the fight,\Nyou'll just end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just wander around\Nthe Dark Forest for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sir Matoriv! I've completed the bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. Do over. The design sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The design?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for a more sophisticated shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to get blown up,\Nso who cares about the design?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Looks like you're making progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Matoriv!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you can cut the unseen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,your blade will become\Nthree, or even five times more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Him? He's probably dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That little brat. What a pampered weenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His type never try\Nunless they're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I left him\Non the other side of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:15:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan was always too soft for his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He could never properly train\Na crybaby like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs my kind of tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sadist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Disciples of Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long do you think\Nyou can hide from me?! Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't think your Princess\Nis safe all frozen, do you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unfortunately, her life force\Nis getting drained in this ice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your Princess's life ends\Ntomorrow at sundown!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry on back! Come on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona's going to die?!\NI won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:16:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real! I'm not dragging everyone down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you defeat Flazzard\Nby sundown tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Princess's life force will be drained\Nby the Forbidden Magic ice and she'll die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But charging in during the day\Nis just what the enemy wants.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We strike tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Light the fuse,\Nand in five seconds... Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have two, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to use\Nthe ugly bombs after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If these don't work, we'll have to\Ndestroy them by sword or magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!\NI made them! They're foolproof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why we're worried.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How will we get to Valge Island?\NOur Balloon Ship has sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a small boat I use for fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fly it across with my magic,\Njust above the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll get us over the whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. But the boat only holds four.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'll be me and Maam and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, of course! I built the bombs!\NOf course I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting for the Princess is\Nwhat the Papnica Troika are for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo, you shouldn't move yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let Dai and his friends\Ncarry our burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go in your stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth seat is already taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.\NI couldn't get a clear image of the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it to the Papnica temple\Nwith my Rura spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but from there it was a real pain\Nand it took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You're the fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats Maam's Behoimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last help you'll get from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be easy with Rura,\Nbut I've never been to that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If Popp does it, he'll take you to the top\Nof Valge Tower inside the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything, Matoriv.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the thanks for when you win, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I swear we'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if I survive this,\NI'd like to continue my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I quit after all that,\Nit'd look like I ran off like some coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd let you run.\NI'm still not finished with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Mentor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "Mentor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan is my one and only master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A master and mentor are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you splitting hairs like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When did Gomechan sneak onboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with the blessing\Nof the great gods of Papnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die out there,\Nforgotten mementos of Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fast!\NWe'll make it to the island in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they don't call him\Na Grand Sorcerer for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,how do we stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to think about how they'd stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll crash! We'll crash! We'll crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagi!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! A Bagi spell as a brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast Bagi, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have Bagi\Nin your Magic Bullet Gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Use Bagi! Use Bagi! Use Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagi!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He talks big, but he always\Nscrews up where it counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to cast Bagi and it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the Dark Flame Spire\Nwith Baduck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Maam and I'll take\Nthe Dark Ice Spire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the two Spires are destroyed\Nand the field is down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we charge into Valge Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. Come with us, Gomechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay safe, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come. The sad little flies\Ninto the spider's web.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystvearn, are your soldiers ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:25.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:32.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:43.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:46.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:52.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:57.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:01.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:07.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:13.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:19.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and his friends managed\Nto reach Valge Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They split up\Nand headed for the two Spires.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, waiting for them there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is the full force of the Dark Army\Nthat anticipated the attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Dai and his friends fall into peril,\Nan unexpected individual appears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Death-Defying Savior"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:23:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:03.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,
